    "In SR, VTM is mainly used to automate the search stage and, sometimes, for screening/ selecting primary studies (Felizardo et al. 2012).",
    "In summary, the integration of NLP techniques in SR automation follows a sequence of processes known as the NLP pipeline, as illustrated in Fig. 2.",
